title: Kylie Jenner 'spent a lot of time with Drake at his 33rd birthday party'
text:
She is back on the market after splitting from Travis Scott.

But it looks like Kylie Jenner may already have her eye on someone new.

The reality star, 22, spent a lot of time with Drake while attending his 33rd birthday bash on Wednesday night, sources told Us Weekly.

New romance? Drake and Kylie Jenner were practically attached at the hip at the rapper's 33rd birthday bash on Wednesday

'She spent the most time near Drake and his friends,' an insider told the website. 'Kylie was rapping to songs and dancing with her friends while she was next to Drake, but they weren’t dancing together, they seemed to have a connection though.'

Insiders noted the pair were having a blast laughing and cracking jokes together while ringing in his big day.

Their attraction for one another was also noted.

'They were joking around and Kylie was laughing. She seemed to be really happy and in a great mood and her and Drake seemed very comfortable with each other. There seemed to be an attraction there,' a second insider said.

Party time! The reality star was spotted leaving the rapper's birthday bash held at Goya Studios in Hollywood

Celebrate! The rapper's birthday was attended by the likes of Adele and even his ex, Rihanna (pictured June 2019)

The newly single star 'really seemed to be living her single best life,' a source said.

A potential Kylie and Drake romance would be a bit awkward for the reality star's family, who have previously feuded with the rapper in the past.

Kanye West has had a long-standing rivalry with Drake, and last year the rapper lashed out at the Hotline Bling singer after learning he had been following his wife Kim Kardashian on Instagram.

Sparks flying: An insider told Us Weekly, 'There seemed to be an attraction there'

Recently, however, Kanye revealed he attempted to bury the hatchet with Drake, and left his phone number at the rapper's house.

'I walk over to Drake's house with no security and leave my phone number, like, "Here's my phone number." I'm not trying to ring the door bell, he might be busy. He got a studio in there, just think he recording at all times,' Kanye said on Apple Beats 1 radio.

Kylie was just one of many stars celebrating Drake's 33rd birthday at Goya studios in Hollywood.

Adele, French Montana, and even Drake's ex, Rihanna.

Kylie, meanwhile, is back on the market after splitting from her long-term boyfriend Travis after two years and a daughter together.
description: The reality star, 22, was seen practically attached at the hip with Drake while attending his 33rd birthday bash on Wednesday night, sources told Us Weekly. The party took place at Goya Studios.
